    <title>Python Data Science Handbook 读书笔记 Numpy 篇</title>
    <url>/2021/02/23/PythonDataScienceHandbook-Numpy/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Numpy-入门"><a href="#Numpy-入门" class="headerlink" title="Numpy 入门"></a>Numpy 入门</h1><p>Numpy 牺牲了一些灵活性，采用了固定类型的数组来高效地储存和运算。</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>不同于 Python lists，Numpy array 中所有元素都具有相同类型。</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 强制类型转换</span></span><br><span class="line">np.array([<span class="number">3.14</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([ 3.14,  4.  ,  2.  ,  3.  ])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 制定Numpy变量类型</span></span><br><span class="line">np.array([<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>], dtype=<span class="string">&#x27;float32&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([ 1.,  2.,  3.,  4.], dtype=float32)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h2 id="创建-Numpy-array"><a href="#创建-Numpy-array" class="headerlink" title="创建 Numpy array"></a>创建 Numpy array</h2><ol>
<li>将 Python list 转化为 Numpy array；</li>
<li>利用函数构造 Numpy array，这对大型数组来说效率较高。</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 嵌套列表转化为高维数组</span></span><br><span class="line">np.array([<span class="built_in">range</span>(i, i + <span class="number">3</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> [<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([[2, 3, 4],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [4, 5, 6],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [6, 7, 8]])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 几个常用的函数</span></span><br><span class="line">np.zeros()</span><br><span class="line">np.ones()</span><br><span class="line">np.full()</span><br><span class="line">np.empty()</span><br><span class="line">np.eye()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">np.arange()</span><br><span class="line">np.linspace()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">np.random.random()</span><br><span class="line">np.random.normal()</span><br><span class="line">np.random.randint()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="指定-Numpy-数据类型"><a href="#指定-Numpy-数据类型" class="headerlink" title="指定 Numpy 数据类型"></a>指定 Numpy 数据类型</h2><ol>
<li>使用 str 指定，<code>np.zeros(10, dtype=&#39;int16&#39;)</code>；</li>
<li>使用 Numpy 对象也可，<code>np.zeros(10, dtype=np.int16)</code>。</li>
</ol>
<p>Numpy 标准数据类型详见<a class="link"   href="https://numpy.org/" >Numpy documentation<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>。</p>
]]></content>
